To read the .plk file, please use the pickle package. For the usage of the 
pickle package, please refer to 

https://docs.python.org/3/library/pickle.html

The items that we can read are as follows, 


'Eng_spd':       engine speed
'Eng_trq'        engine torque
'Eng_pwr':       engine power
'Eng_pwr_opt':   engine optimal power
'Mot_spd':       motor speed
'Mot_trq'        motor torque
'Mot_pwr':       motor power
'Gen_spd':       generator speed 
'Gen_trq':       generator torque
'Gen_pwr':       generator power
'Batt_pwr':      battery power
'T': time        step
